description:
Explore and navigate the world with confidence using Google Maps. Find the best routes with live traffic data and real-time GPS navigation for driving, walking, cycling and public transport. Discover over 250 million businesses and places – from restaurants and shops to everyday essentials – with photos, reviews and helpful information.

Navigate the world, the way that you want:
• Get to where you need to go with fuel-efficient route options
• Find the best route with real-time, turn-by-turn voice and on-screen navigation
• Save time with automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Catch the bus, train and ride-share effortlessly, with real-time updates
• Find bike or scooter rentals to get around more easily

Plan trips and experiences effortlessly:
• Preview an area before you go (e.g. parking, entrances) with Street View
• Use Immersive View to experience what landmarks, parks and routes look like, and even check the weather so that you can be ready in advance
• Create custom lists of your favourite saved places and share with others
• Order delivery and takeaway, make reservations and book hotels
• Don't get lost with offline maps in an area with bad signal
• Search for local places and things to do, and decide based on user reviews and photos

Discover and explore like a local:
• Explore with confidence knowing 500 million users contribute and keep the map up to date each year
• Avoid the crowds by seeing how busy a place is before you get there
• Use Lens in Maps to see walking directions overlaid on the real world
• Filter restaurants by cuisine, hours, price, rating and more
• Ask questions about a place, from dishes to parking, and get quick answers

Some features not available in all countries or cities
Navigation isn't intended to be used by oversized or emergency vehicles

Know what's ahead on the road with the help from other drivers. Waze is a live map that harnesses the local knowledge of tens of millions of drivers around the world. Drivers safely and confidently reach their everyday destinations thanks to Waze map’s GPS navigation, live traffic updates, real-time safety alerts (including roadworks, accidents, crashes, police, potholes and more) and accurate ETAs.


Make your next drive more predictable and stress-free:
• Get there faster with real-time directions, accurate ETAs and automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Even if you know the way, avoid surprises on the road ahead with safety alerts for accidents, crashes, roadworks, objects on the road, potholes, speed bumps, sharp curves, bad weather, emergency vehicles, railway crossings and more
• Steer clear of tickets by knowing where police and red light and speed cameras are located
• Share what’s happening on the road with other drivers by reporting live incidents and hazards
• Stay informed of upcoming speed limit changes, and keep your speedometer in check
• Know which lane to be in with multi-lane guidance
• See toll pricing and choose to avoid tolls along your routes
• Add road passes and vignettes for HOV lanes and restricted traffic zones
• Find petrol/fuel stations and prices and EV charging stations along your route
• Locate car parks near your destination
• Use voice-guided turn-by-turn navigation from a variety of languages, local accents and your favourite celebrities
• Plan your next drive by checking ETAs by future departure or arrival times
• Use your favourite audio apps (for podcasts, music, news, audiobooks) directly within Waze
• Sync Waze to your car’s built-in display through Apple CarPlay


* Some features are not available in all countries


* Waze navigation is not intended for emergency or oversized vehicles


You can manage your in-app Waze privacy settings at any time. Learn more about the Waze privacy policy here, www.waze.com/legal/privacy.

Locato is a powerful and reliable GPS phone tracker that allows you to track and locate your loved ones in real-time. With Locato, you can ensure the safety of your family and friends by knowing their exact whereabouts at all times. Our app provides real-time location updates, comprehensive location history, and smart geo-fence notifications to keep you connected with those who matter most.

Key Features:

Real-Time Location Tracking: Know the current location of your loved ones on a live map.
Accurate GPS Tracking: Find the exact location of your family members and friends in real-time.
Location History: Access past location data to see where they've been.
Geofence Zones: Set up geofence zones to receive notifications when someone enters or leaves a specific area.
Device Tracking: Find lost or stolen phones using another family member's registered device.
Place Alerts: Get notified when family members arrive or leave specific locations like home or school.
Privacy and Consent: Location sharing is only possible with mutual consent to ensure privacy.
How It Works:

Add your family members' phone numbers to the app.
They accept the invite and share their location.
Track their location on the map in real-time.
Why Locato?

Easy Setup: Simply add your loved ones by their phone number and start tracking.
Peace of Mind: Ensure your family members are safe at all times.
Lost Phone Recovery: Track your lost or stolen phone using the app.

Subscription Information:
Locato offers a premium subscription plan with additional features, including unlimited location alerts, extended location history, and an ad-free experience. # E6B+ E6B Flight Calculator 2025! The Essential Tool for Every Pilot

Conquer the skies with E6B+ E6B Flight Calculator, the ultimate flight computer app that makes complex aviation calculations quick and accurate (yes, really!). We've got everything you need, whether you're a student pilot learning the ropes, an experienced commercial aviator, or a flight instructor showing the way.

Here's why E6B+ is the best flight calculator out there:

* Super Easy to Use: Intuitive interface designed by pilots, for pilots - just a few taps for accurate results!

* Over 25 Aviation Functions: Calculate density altitude, true airspeed, compass heading, crosswind components, leg time, fuel requirements - all in one powerful app!

* Lightning-Fast Unit Conversions: Nautical/Statute Miles, Feet/Meters, Pounds/Kilograms, Gallons/Liters - no more headaches with different units!

* Multi-Timezone Clock and Timer: Simultaneously track Zulu, Local and Home time zones - perfect for international flights!

* Precise Fuel Calculations: Calculate fuel requirements, maximum endurance, and consumption rates - never worry about running out mid-flight!

* Navigation Assistance: Compute ground speed, wind direction, wind speed and more - like having a virtual co-pilot!

* MAC & Center of Gravity: Calculate precise percent MAC - crucial for flight safety!

* Descent Planning Calculator: Determine optimal top of descent and required descent rates - smooth landings every time!

* Works Offline: No internet connection needed - works perfectly at 35,000 feet or in remote areas!

* Multi-Device Compatibility: Works seamlessly across iPhone, iPad, Apple Watch and Mac - your data syncs across all devices!

Download E6B+ E6B Flight Calculator today and experience the difference! From classroom to cockpit, this is the must-have tool for every modern pilot.

Disclaimer: This app is for informational purposes only. It should not be used as the sole tool for flight planning and navigation. Always follow aviation regulations and use official sources. Fly safe!

Moovit is one app for all your urban mobility and transport rides!

Dailymail - "This travel app is a godsend for anyone using public transport – with live updates to bus schedules, as well as a great route-planner for cities across the UK."

Transportation is an integral part of urban living. Whether you ride the train, subway/underground /tube, bus, light rail, ferry or metro, use bikes, ride-sharing like Uber, getting the best urban mobility information is critical. Moovit guides you from point A to B in the easiest and most efficient way. Get train and bus times, maps, and live arrival times with ease so you can plan your trip with confidence. Find critical alerts and service disruptions for your favorite lines. Get step-by-step directions of optimal route bus, train, metro, bike or a combination of them. 
This is why Moovit has been named one of the best apps of the year 2017 by the App Store!

Moovit guides more than 865 million users in over 3200 cities throughout the world.

► Journey Planner that combines you all transport options and gives you the best route with live arrivals.

► Live Directions: Get step-by-step directions with live guidance as you travel: know exactly how long you need to walk to your station, how long you’re waiting, view the arrival time of your line and how many stops are left.

► Real time alerts. Know about issues ahead of time by receiving service alerts such as emergency or unexpected disruptions, delays, traffic jams, new construction and more...

► Users reports. Moovit’s users report issues found with stations, line service, and timetables so that we can inform all nearby riders about what’s going on in their area.

► Favorite lines, stations, and places. Get easy access to lines, stations, and places you ride and visit all the time. Plus, get real-time updates if/when there are changes to your favorite lines in case your bus or train time is impacted!

► Bike routes. Get bike routes in addition to the bus, subway, train, or metro trip plans. If you ride bikes (yours or shared) we can plan a route that includes the train or bus. 
Bike docking stations are updated in real-time.

Hello,

* SailFreeGPS displays current location, course (COG), speed (SOG), max speed, Trip distance, speed average and magnetic compass.
* SailFreeGPS displays COG and SOG history (6h) to help you to see trim effect on your sails.
* SailFreeGPS filters GPS information for more accuracy (average of an amount of last measures you can set).
* SailFreeGPS can share your position, COG, SOG to your friends.
* SailFreeGPS helps you during Man OverBoard maneuver (MOB). It stores the location and lead you to it.
* SailFreeGPS displays your track on google map (48h).
* SailFreeGPS helps you during Regatta with its countdown timer and its departure line
* You can store up to 8 waypoints and activate a GOTO function with ETA (Estimated Time to Arrival computation)
* You can save/load track to/from GPX/KML file
* You can calculate distance and heading 
* You can use it on every boat, motor or sail boat.
* You can now activate an anchor alarm or a course alarm.

I am an amateur sailor who has decided to create this app after a Transatlantic cruise.
I add periodically functionalities to this app when I have some spare time.

Please send me an email for any question or problem : contact@sailfreegps.com

Encourage me to continue by subscribing to premium version.

List of features of Premium Version

Premium version DOES NOT CONTAIN ADS.

GPS INFO Tab:
* Doucle click on SPEED will reset trip, max and ags speed
* Long click on COURSE to display compass
* Double click on coordinates to display/hide position

Graph Tab:
* Double click COG graph to switch to full screen mode

MOB Tab:
* Displays of relative bearing of the MOB
* Displays of tack angles
* Double click graph to switch to full screen mode

Waypoint Tab:
* Up to 200 Waypoints
* Displays of relative bearing of Waypoint
* Displays of tack angles
* Double click graph to switch to full screen mode

Map Tab:
* Displays of SOG and COG (speed & course)
* Your track segments are displayed according to your speed

Anchor alarm:
* Anchor area can be a polygon and you can adjust its shape

Regatta Tab:
* "Gun Button" allows to round seconds to nearest minute
    Ex: 4:03 => 4:00 or 3:58 => 4:00
* Enter exact départure time up to the second
* Displays of time to kill/save continuing the same way (speed and course)
* Displays of ideal speed to cross the line at 0:00 on the same course!!!

Settings Tab:
* Displays reverse color (white on black back)
* You can select Hybrid map
* Select on which duration is calculated the speed scale of your track: last 5min, 15 min or all the track
* Select your tack angle value. It will be displayed on MOB and WAYPOINT tabs

Exit:
* Ask to save the track before Exit

Bonjour RATP is the essential app for all your journeys in Île-de-France.
Plan your trips, check live traffic, purchase your tickets, and discover all mobility alternatives around you - metro, RER, bus, tram, Transilien trains, and self-service bikes.

Your routes across all networks.
Metro, RER, bus, tramway, Transilien SNCF trains, Optile… Wherever you are, Bonjour RATP finds the best journey to get you around the entire region.

Journeys tailored to you. 
Customize your search according to your preferences:
- Avoid certain lines or stations,
- Prioritize your preferred modes (metro, RER, Transilien, bus…),
- Minimize transfers or favor accessible routes.
Because every resident of Île-de-France has their own way of traveling.

Real-time traffic and personalized alerts.
Check the network status at a glance and receive real-time alerts in case of disruptions on your favorite lines across the entire Île-de-France network.

All your tickets in your pocket. 
No more monthly queues! Buy the following tickets in the app and access them directly on your iPhone or Navigo pass:
- Navigo Month
- Navigo Week
- Navigo Day
- Metro-Train-RER tickets
- Bus-Tram tickets
- Paris Region-Airports tickets
- Special tickets (Music Festival, Anti-pollution pass...)
- Paris Visite pass

Always on time.
Check real-time schedules for upcoming departures on all your lines. Never miss your bus, metro, or RER again. An incident on your lines? Thanks to alerts, you’ll be immediately informed and the app will suggest an alternative.

Speak and go (Beta)
Just say where you want to go, and Bonjour RATP takes care of the rest!
Voice search makes your journeys even easier.

Bike sharing
Want to ride? Find a bike in seconds. Bonjour RATP shows availability of Vélib’, Lime, and Dott.

Why choose Bonjour RATP?
- Complete coverage across all Île-de-France
- Customizable routes based on your preferences and habits
- Real-time traffic and alerts
- All tickets and passes directly in the app
- All self-service bikes available
- Smooth, clear, and intuitive interface

For more information about our services, feel free to contact us by email at clients@bonjour-ratp.fr

With at bus you can plan your trip, save places, stops and lines, check the status of services and buy all our tickets and passes.

SEARCH

Search for lines, bus stops and schedules wherever you are.

- Find the times of buses at your favourite stops and live departure times, where this service is available
- Check the status of services that you use regularly
- See nearby bus stops and sales points directly on the map

BUY

at bus is your online ticket office, open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
You can purchase all types of tickets and passes.
How? With my at!

- For tickets and carnets all you need is a my at account. If you have not already created one on our website, you can sign up directly in the app
- For passes, you can import a profile registered on our webshop shop.at-bus.it, by inserting your date of birth and tax code

TRAVEL

Once you have purchased the right ticket for your trip, all you have to do is get on board.

- Search where you need to get to and select the best solution for you; the app will notify you when it’s time to depart
- Follow the directions to get to the right stop by foot, monitor live departure times and track the number of stops on the map until you reach your destination
- Save your favorite places so you always have them at your fingertips for next time

MapFactor Navigator is a free GPS navigation app with free offline maps from OpenStreetMaps (incl. free monthly maps update). You can navigate without an internet connection in 200+ countries. Intuitive voice turn-by-turn navigation in different languages, speed limits, camera warnings and many other useful features.

Key features of the MapFactor GPS Navigation app:
- voice navigation in various languages
- door-to-door route planning
- overview of the upcoming manoeuvre and distance shown on the screen
- free offline maps with postcodes (full GB postcodes) installed on your device
- points of interest
- speed limit and camera warnings 
- favourite routes and places
- 2D/3D mode allows realistic visual maps display
- day/night map mode
- routing modes for car, bus, pedestrian, bicycle, motocycle
- route avoidance - block certain road from your route
- maps rotate in driving direction, or north up
- blue motorway signs
- CarPlay connectivity (beta)

Premium Features:
- Head-Up Display
- Alternative Routes
- Remote commands
- No Ads

Live HD Traffic:
- reach your destination stress free, avoid any traffic problem
- all traffic problems at a glance on the map or in a table

OSM maps are created and updated by the community of volunteers at www.osm.org. OSM maps are updated every month for FREE.

Optional professional TomTom navigation maps with UK postcodes available - more reliable and accurate for vehicles navigation. Car version or Truck version with enhanced information for large vehicles.

If you wish to get help or provide feedback to our GPS navigation app, please email ios@mapfactor.com.

«Максим» — это удобные поездки с частными водителями, доставка, грузоперевозки. Ежедневно помогаем миллионам людей экономить деньги на такси, поездках и в путешествиях. Просто выберите подходящий тариф или услугу. 
«Эконом», «Срочный», «Комфорт» — на каждый день. «Эконом» часто выбирают для поездок по межгороду — это отличная возможность доехать с комфортом, но дешевле, чем «Такси».  
«Такси» — современный заказ традиционного такси. 
«Минивэн» и «Автобус» для путешествий большой компанией.
«Грузовые» и «Грузчик» для перевозки вещей на любое расстояние и легкого переезда. Еще с погрузкой может помочь водитель.
«Курьер» и «Купим и привезем», чтобы экономить время, отправлять и получать посылки, товары, еду или лекарства в комфортное время в удобном месте — дома, на работе или в гостях. 
Посмотрите полный список в приложении и оцените все возможности.

Пожелания к заказу
Дополнительно можно выбрать время, когда нужна услуга или такси, добавить информацию для водителя о получателе посылки, детском кресле для поездок с ребенком, багаже. Укажите еще один номер для связи, чтобы создать заказ со своего телефона, но для другого человека. Водитель свяжется с ним, если понадобится уточнить детали поездки.  
Запустите приложение на умных часах с Apple Watch, чтобы следить за статусом заказа.

Удобная оплата
Стоимость поездки или услуги видна сразу, и это удобно для планирования расходов. Легко получить скидку на первые поездки по промокоду MAXX. Оплачивать удобно наличными, картой или переводом, водитель получит оплату моментально. 

Безопасность
Свободные машины и движение водителя на адрес заказа отображаются на карте. В пути можно поделиться треком поездки. Это важно для родителей, которые хотят быть спокойными за детей.
Кнопка SOS позволит ощущать себя в максимальной безопасности во время поездки. Достаточно нажать и отправить всем экстренным контактам свое местоположение или позвонить в службу спасения.

Города, где можно заказать такси или поездку в maxim 
Адлер, Архангельск, Барнаул, Благовещенск, Владивосток, Владикавказ, Вологда, Грозный, Екатеринбург, Иваново, Иркутск, Казань, Калининград, Кемерово, Кострома, Краснодар, Красноярск, Курган, Курск, Липецк, Магнитогорск, Москва, Мурманск, Набережные Челны, Нижний Тагил, Новокузнецк, Новосибирск, Омск, Орел, Оренбург, Пенза, Петрозаводск, Ростов-на-Дону, Рязань, Самара, Санкт-Петербург, Саранск, Смоленск, Сочи, Ставрополь, Стерлитамак, Сургут,  Сыктывкар, Таганрог, Тамбов, Тверь, Томск, Тула, Тюмень, Улан-Удэ, Ульяновск, Уфа, Хабаровск, Чебоксары, Челябинск, Череповец, Чита, Якутск, Ярославль и др.

Работаем с 2003 года
Одно из первых в мире приложений для заказа поездок, доставки, такси, перевозки грузов
